metadata.name: Margie Winston
metadata.description:
Margie grew up and studied magic in the Shkar forest that is located in the west continent. She was born into a family of a cat woman and a magician.
 From the age of 5, she began studying at the school of magic and became the earliest graduate. At the age of 13, she decided to make a long adventure for searching mentors of great magic. 
She managed to visit the most far corners of the world, face various dangers, visit the most ancient libraries of the southern region.
During 8 years of wandering, Margie discovered many talents in herself, but also met many difficulties and dangers. Margie has saw death two of her close friends, the wounds after this loss will remain with her forever.

Now she is 22 and lives near the place where she grew up, where her parents live. Margie runs a magic shop where she sells curiosities from all over the world. The guys who come to her shop most often are students at the magic school where she once studied.
